descriptionMarkdown:
red wire input signals:      
p==0 shut down no matter what.   
m!=0 run the build no matter what  except when p==0.   
p>=3 may the power to the build .   

green wire input :    
the amount of output product in storage/buffer 
thresholds are 50k and 1,8M ATM


other charge needed to run the build must be in the range of  20-85  
if  charge gets under 20 build will shut down to prevent catastrophic power down spiral in the base   
there are 2 manual switches :  
left is manual turn on   
right-low is manual turn off even if conditions above are met   
these 2 are for cases when manual intervention might be needed and are radar map friendly
title: circuit that helps consume less power in beaconed or other power demanding builds signal control + manual on/off + emergency signals
